{"tid":583053,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解《大樂師．為愛配樂》票房會咁差","createTime":"2018-03-06T16:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T11:54:04.000Z","uid":13685,"like":103,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"ac713611b1459e770e947604f835a323e2c31946","tid":583053,"uid":13685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"套戲明明咁正<br />\n係近年拍得好好既本土港產片<br />\n想約朋友睇 唔少人未睇已經講<br />\n港產片?不了 幾時香港人變到咁<br />\n賭城風雲呢D咁既同大陸合作既爛片可以咁多人睇 <br />\n真係好嬲點解咁樣 好睇電影咁既票房 <br />\n終於明白呢個世界真係唔公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想同顏卓靈同埋馮志強導演講聲加油 <br />\n呢幾日佢地兩個都去左謝票<br />\n其實講咁多都係想各位留意返多D本土港產片姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fa2b6aa7c4adcc8ab2454090c9bd12972dcd9b","tid":583053,"uid":50216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"無乜宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b92ad7590937588bd04a89f5804aeb48eb10055","tid":583053,"uid":42848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"年頭啲所謂金像港片全線收皮,藍天白雲,以青春的名義,大樂師,<br />\n通通唔過一百萬,真係難堪"},{"pid":"a93476719d4c452a39b02c4a24fe210f0acea7a2","tid":583053,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"後日得返一場,真係要睇趁而家"},{"pid":"e5343be472dbc2f5a10f01f32950a8ab89327da1","tid":583053,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93476719d4c452a39b02c4a24fe210f0acea7a2","tid":583053,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"後日得返一場,真係要睇趁而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"好想睇，但日日早出晚歸，聽日最晏嗰場得返1745，仲未收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfa0491620f4023e